   <p>See <a href="default.xqy?keys=GEWN-print-03-04-02-0005" class="document">GW to Cooke</a> and <a href="default.xqy?keys=GEWN-print-03-04-02-0012" class="document">to John Sullivan, both this date</a>.</p>

